== 已產品化的智慧型輸入法
* /[Chinese parsing in a phoneme-to-character conversion system based on semantic pattern matching http://iasl.iis.sinica.edu.tw/webpdf/paper-1995-Chinese_Parsing_in_a_Phoneme-to-Character_.pdf]/ : 自然輸入法
* /[Mining Pinyin-to-Character Conversion Rules From Large-Scale Corpus: A Rough Set Approach http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/iel5/3477/28545/01275519.pdf]/ : 微軟拼音（及不知道那一版的 Mac 注音）。作者是哈爾濱工大[ITNLP Lab http://www.insun.hit.edu.cn/]的[王曉龍 http://cs.hitsz.edu.cn/wangxiaolonghomepage.htm]。
* /[Bringing text input beyond the desktop http://portal.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=633324&coll=Portal&dl=ACM&CFID=46660646&CFTOKEN=50330120]/ : T9

== Language Model (n-gram)
=== Roni Rosenfeld
* http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~roni/publication_list.html 的 Statistical/Machine Learning Methods in Speech and Language Processing 部分。
** [Two decades of Statistical Language Modeling: Where Do We Go From Here? http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~roni/papers/survey-slm-IEEE-PROC-0004.pdf]
* 延伸閱讀
** [Maximum Entropy http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~aberger/maxent.html]
** [Conditional Random Fields http://www.inference.phy.cam.ac.uk/hmw26/crf/]

